          eat at. But if you are planning on staying at a hotel, you could either order room service or go out to eat at a nearby 
          restaurant.</h3>
        </p>
        <div>
        </div>
        <p><h2>
          4. Activities</h2> <h3>-Excursions usually cost around $200+, but they are a lot of fun for families & friends to do
          together. Getting a tour of the area that you're in would be a great oppertunity to learn and have some cute photo ops.</h3>
        </p>
